1. *Klavir* je bio prekriven prašinom. (The piano was covered in dust.)
2. Moja sestra svira *klavir*. (My sister plays the piano.)
3. *Klavir* u mom stanu je star preko 50 godina. (The piano in my apartment is over 50 years old.)
4. Moj učitelj muzike je insistirao da učim da sviram na *klaviru*. (My music teacher insisted that I learn to play the piano.)
5. *Klavirski* koncert je bio izvanredan. (The piano concert was outstanding.)
6. Molim te, donesi mi stolicu da mogu da sednem za *klavir*. (Please bring me a chair so I can sit at the piano.)
7. Svirao sam *klavir* celu noć. (I played the piano all night.)
8. Ovo je nova *klavirska* klupa koju sam kupio za svoj *klavir*. (This is a new piano bench that I bought for my piano.)